# Artifact Management Database Configuration

## PostgreSQL / Supabase
# PostgreSQL connection string for Prisma migrations
DATABASE_URL="postgresql://postgres:password@localhost:5432/artifacts?schema=public"

## Supabase (optional - for client-side RLS queries)
SUPABASE_URL="https://your-project.supabase.co"
SUPABASE_ANON_KEY="your-anon-key-here"
SUPABASE_SERVICE_ROLE_KEY="your-service-role-key-here"

## OpenAI (for embeddings - Phase 2+)
OPENAI_API_KEY="sk-..."

## GitHub (for repo sync - Phase 3+)
GITHUB_TOKEN="ghp_..."

## Environment
NODE_ENV="development"
